#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.arange"
msgstr "# triton.language.arange"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:4
msgid "简介：`triton.language.arange`函数用于生成一个从`start`到`end`（不包括`end`）的连续整数序列。"
msgstr "Introduction: The `triton.language.arange` function is used to generate a contiguous sequence of integers from `start` to `end` (excluding `end`)."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.arange(start, end, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                  | 说明                                   |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | ---------------------------- |\n"
"| `start`           | `scalar`               | 创建连续整数序列的起始数值，必须是编译时常量（tl.constexpr） |\n"
"| `end`            | `scalar`               | 创建连续整数序列的结束数值 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type     | Description                                                  |\n"
"| -------------- | -------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| `start`        | `scalar` | The starting value for creating a sequence of consecutive integers; must be a compile-time constant (`tl.constexpr`) |\n"
"| `end`          | `scalar` | The ending value for creating a sequence of consecutive integers |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：连续整数序列的tensor\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: A tensor of consecutive integer sequences.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:20
msgid "结论：要求arange的参数start、end必须是constant，因此无类型，支持类型对应的值范围，最大到int32，硬件指令也只支持到int32。"
msgstr "Conclusion: The parameters `start` and `end` of `arange` must be constants, hence they are untyped, supporting value ranges corresponding to their types, up to `int32`. Hardware instructions also only support up to `int32`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:22
msgid ""
"|                | uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"| --------- | ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"| GPU            | ×    | ×     | ×     | ×     | ×      | √      | ×      | ×     | ×    | ×    | ×    |   ×    |\n"
"| Ascend  A2/A3 | ×    | ×     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×      | ×     | ×    | ×    | ×    |   ×    |\n"
msgstr ""
"|                | uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"| --------- | ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"| GPU            | ×    | ×     | ×     | ×     | ×      | √      | ×      | ×     | ×    | ×    | ×    |   ×    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ×    | ×     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×      | ×     | ×    | ×    | ×    |   ×    |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:24
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:26
msgid ""
"0 =< (end - start) <1048576\n"
"end >= 0,  start  >= 0\n"
msgstr ""
"0 =< (end - start) < 1048576\n"
"end >= 0, start >= 0\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:28
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:30
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:32
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:34
msgid ""
"1.函数用于生成一个[start, end) 的连续整数序列，CUDA要求range=(end-start)必须为2的幂次方。Triton-ascend并无此要求。\n"
"2.NV和Triton-ascend都限制end的最大值TRITON_MAX_TENSOR_NUMEL = 1048576\n"
"3.arange的输入必须是constant常量，支持uint、int类型的小于1048576（最大值TRITON_MAX_TENSOR_NUMEL ）的数值。int64不支持。\n"
"4.arange的start 和 end 应大于等于0。\n"
msgstr ""
"1. The function is used to generate a continuous integer sequence in the range [start, end). CUDA requires that range=(end-start) must be a power of 2. Triton-ascend does not have this requirement.  \n"
"2. Both NV and Triton-ascend limit the maximum value of end to TRITON_MAX_TENSOR_NUMEL = 1048576.  \n"
"3. The input of arange must be a constant, supporting uint and int type values less than 1048576 (the maximum value TRITON_MAX_TENSOR_NUMEL). int64 is not supported.  \n"
"4. The start and end of arange should be greater than or equal to 0.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:38
msgid "以下示例实现了生成一个[0, 128) 的连续整数序列："
msgstr "The following example implements generating a continuous integer sequence from [0, 128):"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Creation_Ops/arange.md:40
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_arange(z, BLOCK: tl.constexpr, START: tl.constexpr, END: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    off = tl.arange(0, BLOCK)\n"
"    val = tl.arange(START, END)\n"
"    tl.store(z + off, val)\n"
"\n"
"@pytest.mark.parametrize('param_list',[[0, 128],])\n"
"def test_case_access(param_list):\n"
"    start, end = param_list\n"
"    shape = [end]\n"
"    block = end - start\n"
"    dtype = 'int32'\n"
"    y_cal = torch.zeros(shape, dtype=torch.int32).npu()\n"
"    triton_arange[(1, )](y_cal, START = start, END = end, BLOCK = block)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

